Even after consuming that miner,

00:25:28.834 --> 00:25:30.154
my first blood bag,

00:25:30.594 --> 00:25:32.793
and my body stabilized,

00:25:33.753 --> 00:25:36.874
and I even learned to blend
into human society,

00:25:37.594 --> 00:25:39.553
the fear remained.

00:25:42.513 --> 00:25:44.473
Do you know when

00:25:45.033 --> 00:25:46.273
my fear finally faded?

