00:31:07.154 --> 00:31:08.394
Alright, Miss Nie.

00:31:08.834 --> 00:31:09.954
Time for some exercise.

00:31:10.674 --> 00:31:11.513
What exercise?

00:31:12.473 --> 00:31:13.194
To rehabilitate.

00:31:13.594 --> 00:31:15.073
Mr. Yan ordered the equipment.

00:31:15.594 --> 00:31:16.634
I've been busy with it

00:31:16.793 --> 00:31:17.713
all this morning.

00:31:54.513 --> 00:31:55.154
Shift change.

00:31:55.713 --> 00:31:58.313
I just fell asleep.

00:31:58.753 --> 00:32:00.434
Stop whining. Get up.

00:32:01.253 --> 00:32:01.753
Bro.

00:32:01.753 --> 00:32:02.273
Up!

00:32:02.273 --> 00:32:03.154
Bro.

00:32:03.154 --> 00:32:03.753
It hurts.

00:32:04.154 --> 00:32:04.713
It hurts.

00:32:04.993 --> 00:32:06.154
I've been searching forever.

00:32:06.354 --> 00:32:07.713
Fine, I'll go.

00:32:09.793 --> 00:32:10.753
Sleep carefully.

00:32:10.753 --> 00:32:11.553
It's full of bugs.

00:32:21.753 --> 00:32:23.273
Before Mr. Yan left,

00:32:23.753 --> 00:32:25.793
